[size=16pt][b][color=#9333ea]ABOUT Q-NARWHALKNIGHT[/color][/b][/size]

Q-NarwhalKnight is a next-generation blockchain featuring:

[list]
[li][b]Post-Quantum Cryptography:[/b] Dilithium5 + Kyber1024 (NIST PQC standards)[/li]
[li][b]DAG-BFT Consensus:[/b] Zero-message complexity Byzantine fault tolerance[/li]
[li][b]Narwhal Mempool:[/b] High-throughput reliable broadcast with Bracha's protocol[/li]
[li][b]Built-in DEX:[/b] Automated Market Maker with cross-decimal token support[/li]
[li][b]Smart Contracts:[/b] WASM-based VittuaVM with Solidity-like syntax[/li]
[li][b]AI Integration:[/b] On-chain AI inference with opML verification[/li]
[li][b]Privacy Features:[/b] Bulletproofs, ring signatures, Tor hidden service[/li]
[li][b]Tor Support:[/b] Full .onion hidden service access[/li]
[/list]

[b]Technical specs:[/b]
[list]
[li]Written in Rust (200,000+ lines)[/li]
[li]4,000+ automated tests[/li]
[li]3-server HA deployment with zero-downtime upgrades[/li]
[li]Post-quantum secure from genesis block[/li]
[/list]

