[size=16pt][b][color=#9333ea]MERKLE-VERIFIED REWARDS[/color][/b][/size]

All bounty scores are anchored in a Merkle tree for cryptographic verifiability:

[list]
[li]Every score update is recorded on-chain[/li]
[li]Final scores produce a Merkle root published to the blockchain[/li]
[li]Participants can independently verify their reward allocation[/li]
[li]Tamper-proof and transparent distribution[/li]
[li]Sybil resistance with social verification[/li]
[/list]

